<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">To carry out this division (except chapter 3041) and chapter 3121, there is established in the Treasury the Historic Preservation Fund.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idefa1c388-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db">(<ref href="/us/pl/113/287/s3">Pub. L. 113–287, § 3</ref>, <date date="2014-12-19">Dec. 19, 2014</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/128/3206">128 Stat. 3206</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
